race.description: The Don Moore Memorial Mdn Plate
race.comment: BETTA BEING SINGLE (5) is back from a lengthy spell but looks up to the mark for this with two recent trial hit-outs and gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim. Only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a major role in the outcome. EXCELOQUENT (10) didn't measure up in the rich Magic Millions debut race before being tipped out for time to furnish. Has since won her past two trials and will find this assignment much easier than that debut effort. Keep very safe. HELLARIOUS (13) was well in the betting when facing the starter for the first time and where there's smoke there's fire. Worth following up. Former Victorian GUNNIE GUNFIGHTER (2) is having his first run for the new stable and any market support must be noted. HASANA (14) strips fitter second-up from the break and may add some value to the exotics.
